Hello there!

If you're here either you found me on github, in a discord, or similar. 
Either way, you may or may not know who I am. I'm a programmer, musician,
camera guy, and just a tech nerd!

You might see me around game development spaces, minecraft (occasionally, though not often), or around [Legundo's](https://youtube.com/@legundo) community.
I'm a developer and systems administrator for him so I'm decently active in that space.

This blog will mainly be for my thoughts on anything technical, when or if I feel like posting. 
There's also an [RSS](https://ryzech.net/index.xml) feed if anyone wants to be notified of new posts here, although it won't be very frequent.

Hope whoever's reading this has a nice day, and stay safe. <3


